```

---

# 9️⃣ Dump memory of Chrome process

Use the PID of chrome (example **2380**).

```bash
vol -f memory.raw -o chrome_dum windows.memmap --pid 2380 --dump
```

Now check dumped files.

```bash
cd chrome_dum
ls
```

You will see:

```
pid.2380.dmp
```

