# 14️⃣ Fix corrupted PNG

Check the script:

```bash
cat fix.py
```

Edit the script:

```bash
nano fix.py
```

Code inside:

```python
import zlib
d = open("clue.png","rb").read()
i = next(i for i in range(len(d)) if d[i]==0x78 and d[i+1] in (1,156,218))
print(zlib.decompress(d[i:]).decode())
```

Run it:

```bash
python3 fix.py
```

This reveals **first half of the flag**.

